('985b24ff-d7a1-4aad-8e27-5187c38fdaf4', 'Recon Marine Action Figure', 'Outside of outright planetary invasion, the UEE Marines'' Recon Division train extensively in infiltration operations when a smaller footprint is needed. These highly-trained soldiers are experts in sabotage, intelligence gathering, and close-quarter combat. This exclusive figure in Takuetsu''s Military Might series depicts one of these ghost-like marines. Adorned in period accurate combat suit, this Recon Marine''s ready to cause trouble wherever you put them.', NULL, 1, 1, 0.25, 'UNDEFINED', 'Ship.Flair.Flair_Surface', ARRAY['Flair','ActionFigure'], '{"className":"Flair_Actn_Figure_UEE_Recon_Marine_Cen","reference":"985b24ff-d7a1-4aad-8e27-5187c38fdaf4","itemName":"flair_actn_figure_uee_recon_marine_cen","type":"Flair_Surface","subType":"UNDEFINED","size":1,"grade":1,"name":"Recon Marine Action Figure","tags":"Flair ActionFigure","classification":"Ship.Flair.Flair_Surface","stdItem":{"UUID":"985b24ff-d7a1-4aad-8e27-5187c38fdaf4","ClassName":"Flair_Actn_Figure_UEE_Recon_Marine_Cen","Size":1,"Grade":1,"Width":0.15,"Height":0.15,"Length":0.15,"InventoryOccupancy":{"Dimensions":{"Width":0.15,"Length":0.15,"Height":0.15},"UIDimensions":{"Width":0.75,"Length":0.75,"Height":0.75},"Volume":{"SCU":0,"SCUConverted":1,"Unit":"µSCU"}},"Mass":0.25,"Type":"Flair_Surface.UNDEFINED","Name":"Recon Marine Action Figure","Description":"Outside of outright planetary invasion, the UEE Marines’ Recon Division train extensively in infiltration operations when a smaller footprint is needed. These highly-trained soldiers are experts in sabotage, intelligence gathering, and close-quarter combat. This exclusive figure in Takuetsu’s Military Might series depicts one of these ghost-like marines. Adorned in period accurate combat suit, this Recon Marine’s ready to cause trouble wherever you put them.","DescriptionText":"Outside of outright planetary invasion, the UEE Marines'' Recon Division train extensively in infiltrati